column1: *: sars.cov.2_cocentration_copy_per_m. This is the mean concentration of SAR-CoV-2 from N1 and N2 primers using RT-qPCR
**: pmmov_concentration. This is the mean relative cocentration of PMMoV from Ct values of two technical replicates using RT-qPCR.

***: new_cases or cumulative cases. This is the daily new COVID-19 cases or cumulative cases on the day when samples were collected. Data were downloaded from https://usafacts.org/visualizations/coronavirus-covid-19-spread-map/
****: wwtp_flow_MGD. This is the mean flow rate for the facilities where wastewater samples were collected
